salm cakir, ilul g 1950 di iɛzzuzn, laṛbɛa n ayt iratn, g tiɣrmt n tizi wzzu d amsnils (Linguiste) adzayri ,d aslmad n tutlayt tmaziɣt di tsdawit n fransa. cakir isswuri g usinag amaḍlan n tutlayin d tɣrmiwin tugmiḍin (INALCO) di bariz sg asgg°as 1989, di wmkan n andri bassut (André Bassot) d lyunil galand (Liounel Galand]]. di usgg°as 1973 yuwey d aduktuṛa di tsnilsit tamattut. sakkin, sg 1973 d 1981,d aslmad g tsdawit n dzayr tamanaɣt. g 1978, yuwey aduktuṛa niḍn g tskla d tussniwin talsiyin. gr asgg°as 1981 d 1989, d aslmad di tmdint n Aix-en-Provence g tsdawit n Provence akd wammas amaḍlan n urzzu adlsan [Cnrs]). sakkin, di 1990, yssbded ammas n urzzu amaziɣ "André Basset" di tsdawit n inalku (INLACO) g usgg°as 2008, yebda tawuri g usudu n urzzu xf umaḍal aɛṛab d anuslm n Aix-Provence. cakir yura aṭṭas n idlisn d tzrawin xf tsnilsit tamaziɣt. daɣen, d ntta ay d yelhan s tasnayt tamaziɣt (Encyclopédie Amazigh) nna d ittffɣn di tmurt n fransa. gr idlisn nna yssuffɣ: imaziɣn ass ad g usgg°as 1989, manwil d Linguistique Amazigh (awfus n tsnilsit tamaziɣt, g 1991).

==Tameddurt Tasdawant==

Deg 1973, yuwey-d aduktuṛa deg Tesnilst Tamatut. Sakkin, seg 1973 d 1981, yeqdec d aselmad deg tesdawit n temdint n Lezzayer. Deg 1978, yuwey-d aduktuṛa nniḍen deg Tsekla d Tussniwin Talsanin. Gar 1981 e 1989, yeqdec d aselmad deg temdint n [[Aix-en-Provence]] (deg tesdawit n Provence akked Wammas Aɣelnaw n Unadi Ussnan [CNRS]). 
Sakkin, deg 1990, yessbed-d Ammas n Unadi Amaziɣ "André Basset" deg tesdawit n INALCO. Ma deg 2008, yebda iqeddec deg Usudu n Unadi ɣef Yimaḍalen Aɛṛab ed Yineslem n Aix-Provence. Salem Caker yura-d aṭas n yedlisen ed tezrawin (études) ɣef tesnilsit (linguistique) tamaziɣt. Daɣen, d netta ay d-yelhan s [[Tasedkalt Tamaziɣt|Tsedkalt Tamaziɣt]] (Encyclopédie Berbère) ay d-itteffɣen deg Fransa.

